                        <interp inst="t18540102-name-304" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. These 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. are bad, three of them are from one mould.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had been drinking with some friends; I changed half a sovereign; I do not know where, but I must have taken the 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. then.</p>
